channel.title: Return Codes
channel.description:
Does anyone know what [u]each[/u] return code says(*)? return = 3, etc.. Does anyone know? Thanks.
*:What it says on the client, like #1 might say, no response from server, try another world. etc

item.title: Return Codes
item.dc:creator: @Java_Is_My_Bitch Java Is My Bitch™
item.description:
@Java_Is_My_Bitch wrote:

[quote=“MC Gower, post:2, topic:150017”]1 = idk
2 = login
3 = Invalid username or password
4 = Your account has been disabled
5 = Your account is already logged in
6 = Server has been updated
7 = World is full
8 = Unable to connect (login server off-line)
9 = Login limit exceeded
10 = Unable to connect (bad session id)
11 = Login server rejected
12 = You need a members account
13 = Could not complete login
14 = The server is being updated
15 = idk
16 = Login attempts exceeded
17 = You are standing in a members-only area
20 = Invalid login server requested
21 = You have only just left another world
-1 = No response from loginserver[/quote][quote=“aftereffect, post:1, topic:150029”][quote author=MC Gower link=topic=205488.msg1809908#msg1809908 date=1191815866]
1 = idk
2 = login
3 = Invalid username or password
4 = Your account has been disabled
5 = Your account is already logged in
6 = Server has been updated
7 = World is full
8 = Unable to connect (login server off-line)
9 = Login limit exceeded
10 = Unable to connect (bad session id)
11 = Login server rejected
12 = You need a members account
13 = Could not complete login
14 = The server is being updated
15 = idk
16 = Login attempts exceeded
17 = You are standing in a members-only area
20 = Invalid login server requested
21 = You have only just left another world
-1 = No response from loginserver
[/quote]Heres a better one,
0 - Starts login process.
1 - Calls the login void.
2 - Make a new player.
3 - Invalid username or password.
4 - Your account has been disabled.
5 - Your account is already logged in.
6 - RuneScape has been updated!
7 - This world is full.
8 - Unable to connect.
9 - Login limit exceeded.
10 - Unable to connect.
11 - Login server rejected session.
12 - You need a members account to login to this world.
13 - Could not complete login.
14 - The server is being updated.
15 - Not sure.
16 - Login attempts exceeded.
17 - You are standing in a members-only area.
20 - Invalid loginserver requested
21 - You have only just left another world
-1 - No response from loginserver.[/quote]

Thank you much appreciated!
